## Agent Operating System (State-Driven Collaboration Protocol) (2026-03-09)
- **Problem:** AI chats suffer from amnesia and drift, acting as "tool-based customer service" rather than autonomous CEOs.
- **Solution:** Adopted a 6-document framework for all ongoing projects (`roadmap`, `task`, `issue`, `cowork`, `decision`, `learning`).
- **Execution Rules:** 
  - Every session must read these before acting, and write to them when done.
  - "Done" tasks require physical proof (TxHash, PID, File path, etc.).
  - Delegated coding/sweat tasks to Sub-agents instead of cluttering the main strategy channel.

